data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This gorgeous 4-bedroom, is nestled in a tranquil neighborhood with a water view of the James River from the front porch and primary bedroom. Boasting a spacious 3,309 square feet, this home is made for families seeking comfort and style. The heart of the home is the fully equipped kitchen with all SS and a gas range.  The open floor plan allows for plenty of room to entertain and for being together while meals are prepared and served.  The primary bedroom has space for a sitting area or exercise equipment.  Two bedrooms share a common space and the laundry room is upstairs with the bedrooms!  The large fenced in backyard is great for grilling out while kids and dogs can play together.  A large new shed provides extra storage space for all your yard/garden tools.  Don’t miss the opportunity to make this your forever home! Some photos virtually staged.
